NNNNAAAAMMMMEEEE
     elmtag - add taglines to your e-mails

SSSSYYYYNNNNOOOOPPPPSSSSIIIISSSS
     eeeellllmmmmttttaaaagggg [ ----rrrr ] (_r_a_n_d_o_m_l_y-_s_e_l_e_c_t-_a-_t_a_g_l_i_n_e)

DDDDEEEESSSSCCCCRRRRIIIIPPPPTTTTIIIIOOOONNNN
     _E_l_m_t_a_g is an interactive  screen-oriented  tagline  includer
     for your e-mails.

