IIIINNNNSSSSTTTTAAAALLLLLLLLAAAATTTTIIIIOOOONNNN
     There is only two step to make Elmtag.pl ready to work.

  CCCCoooonnnnffffiiiigggguuuurrrriiiinnnngggg EEEEllllmmmmttttaaaagggg....ppppllll
     Open elmtag.pl with a text editor and update  the  fallowing
     file names.

     Location of your tagline database

