     $$$$yyyyoooouuuurrrr____eeeeddddiiiittttoooorrrr ==== ''''vvvviiii'''';;;;

     Do you prefere an alphabeticaly ordered list?

     $$$$aaaallllpppphhhhaaaabbbbeeeettttiiiiccccaaaallll ==== 1111;;;; ((((1111====oooonnnn,,,, 0000====ooooffffffff))))

     centeralize taglines when appending to e-mails?

     $$$$cccceeeennnntttteeeerrrrttttaaaaggggssss ==== 1111;;;; ((((1111====oooonnnn,,,, 0000====ooooffffffff))))

     Elmtag.pl's configuration are done. Now  configure  your  e-
     mail program by fallowing these steps:

  IIIIffff yyyyoooouuuu uuuusssseeee EEEELLLLMMMM
          - Start ELM



